        "type": "dialogue",
        "hoverText": "☉ Speak to the Director",
        "requires": "has_certificate",
        "requiresText": "The Director appears to be napping. A sign on the desk reads: 'DO NOT DISTURB WITHOUT PROPER DOCUMENTATION.'",
        "dialogue": {
          "nodes": [
            {
              "speaker": "T H E   D I R E C T O R",
              "text": "...Hm? What? Oh. A petitioner. I was not sleeping. I was C O N T E M P L A T I N G   P O L I C Y."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "T H E   D I R E C T O R",
              "text": "You have made it all the way here. I am mildly I M P R E S S E D."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "T H E   D I R E C T O R",
              "text": "I need only stamp your certificate and you may go. But first — one final question. A F O R M A L I T Y."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "T H E   D I R E C T O R",
              "text": "What is the P U R P O S E of your visit today?",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "text": "To obtain my certificate",
                  "correct": true,
                  "response": "Ah. Yes. The one you are already holding. How P E C U L I A R. S T A M P E D. You now officially E X I S T. Your name is misspelled. This is S T A N D A R D."
                },
                {
                  "text": "To discover the truth",
                  "correct": false,
                  "response": "Truth is not a service we provide. Department of Philosophy, third corridor on the left. It has been closed since before time was I N V E N T E D."
                },
                {
                  "text": "To restore the Inspektorat",
                  "correct": false,
                  "response": "The Inspektorat does not require restoration. It has never stopped operating. It will never stop operating. Your concern has been F I L E D."
                },
                {
                  "text": "I have forgotten",
                  "correct": false,
                  "response": "You said that last time too. Please state your A C T U A L   P U R P O S E."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        "onSuccess": {
          "type": "notify",
          "text": "T H E   E N D — Your Certificate of Existence has been stamped. Your name is misspelled. Please allow 6-8 eternities for processing. Do N O T file a complaint.",
          "duration": 12000
        }
      }
